text: Multidentia sclerocarpa is a species of flowering plants in the family Rubiaceae. It is found in Kenya and Tanzania. == Sources == * Lovett, J. & Clarke, G.P. 1998. Multidentia sclerocarpa. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
